{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Hello. I would like to start my talk"},{"time":3000,"text":"with actually two questions, and the first one is:"},{"time":5000,"text":"How many people here actually eat pig meat?"},{"time":8000,"text":"Please raise your hand --"},{"time":10000,"text":"oh, that's a lot."},{"time":12000,"text":"And how many people have actually seen"},{"time":14000,"text":"a live pig producing this meat?"},{"time":16000,"text":"In the last year?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"In the Netherlands -- where I come from --"},{"time":21000,"text":"you actually never see a pig, which is really strange,"},{"time":24000,"text":"because, on a population of 16 million people,"},{"time":26000,"text":"we have 12 million pigs."},{"time":29000,"text":"And well, of course, the Dutch can't eat all these pigs."},{"time":31000,"text":"They eat about one-third, and the rest is exported"},{"time":34000,"text":"to all kinds of countries in Europe and the rest of the world."},{"time":37000,"text":"A lot goes to the U.K., Germany."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"And what I was curious about --"},{"time":41000,"text":"because historically, the whole pig would be used up until the last bit"},{"time":44000,"text":"so nothing would be wasted --"},{"time":46000,"text":"and I was curious to find out"},{"time":48000,"text":"if this was actually still the case."},{"time":50000,"text":"And I spent about three years researching."},{"time":52000,"text":"And I followed this one pig"},{"time":54000,"text":"with number \"05049,\""},{"time":56000,"text":"all the way up until the end"},{"time":58000,"text":"and to what products it's made of."},{"time":60000,"text":"And in these years, I met all kinds people"},{"time":62000,"text":"like, for instance, farmers and butchers, which seems logical."},{"time":65000,"text":"But I also met aluminum mold makers,"},{"time":68000,"text":"ammunition producers"},{"time":70000,"text":"and all kinds of people."},{"time":72000,"text":"And what was striking to me"},{"time":74000,"text":"is that the farmers actually had no clue"},{"time":76000,"text":"what was made of their pigs,"},{"time":78000,"text":"but the consumers -- as in us --"},{"time":81000,"text":"had also no idea"},{"time":83000,"text":"of the pigs being in all these products."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85000,"text":"So what I did is,"},{"time":87000,"text":"I took all this research"},{"time":89000,"text":"and I made it into a -- well, basically it's a product catalog of this one pig,"},{"time":92000,"text":"and it carries a duplicate of his ear tag"},{"time":95000,"text":"on the back."},{"time":97000,"text":"And it consists of seven chapters --"},{"time":100000,"text":"the chapters are skin, bones, meat, internal organs,"},{"time":102000,"text":"blood, fat and miscellaneous."},{"time":105000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":107000,"text":"In total,"},{"time":109000,"text":"they weigh 103.7 kilograms."},{"time":111000,"text":"And to show you how often you actually"},{"time":114000,"text":"meet part of this pig in a regular day,"},{"time":116000,"text":"I want to show you some images of the book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"You probably start the day with a shower."},{"time":122000,"text":"So, in soap, fatty acids"},{"time":124000,"text":"made from boiling pork bone fat"},{"time":126000,"text":"are used as a hardening agent,"},{"time":128000,"text":"but also for giving it a pearl-like effect."},{"time":131000,"text":"Then if you look around you in the bathroom,"},{"time":133000,"text":"you see lots more products"},{"time":135000,"text":"like shampoo, conditioner,"},{"time":137000,"text":"anti-wrinkle cream, body lotion,"},{"time":140000,"text":"but also toothpaste."},{"time":142000,"text":"Then, so, before breakfast,"},{"time":144000,"text":"you've already met the pig so many times."},{"time":147000,"text":"Then, at breakfast, the pig that I followed,"},{"time":149000,"text":"the hairs off the pig or proteins from the hairs off the pig"},{"time":152000,"text":"were used as an improver of dough."},{"time":155000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":157000,"text":"Well, that's what the producer says: it's \"improving the dough,"},{"time":159000,"text":"of course.\""},{"time":162000,"text":"In low-fat butter, or actually in many low-fat products,"},{"time":164000,"text":"when you take the fat out, you actually take the taste and the texture out."},{"time":167000,"text":"So what they do is they put gelatin back in,"},{"time":170000,"text":"in order to retain the texture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"Well, when you're off to work, under the road or under the buildings that you see,"},{"time":177000,"text":"there might very well be cellular concrete,"},{"time":179000,"text":"which is a very light kind of concrete"},{"time":181000,"text":"that's actually got proteins from bones inside"},{"time":184000,"text":"and it's also fully reusable."},{"time":187000,"text":"In the train brakes -- at least in the German train brakes --"},{"time":189000,"text":"there's this part of the brake"},{"time":191000,"text":"that's made of bone ash."},{"time":193000,"text":"And in cheesecake and all kinds of desserts,"},{"time":196000,"text":"like chocolate mousse, tiramisu, vanilla pudding,"},{"time":198000,"text":"everything that's cooled in the supermarket,"},{"time":200000,"text":"there's gelatin to make it look good."},{"time":203000,"text":"Fine bone china -- this is a real classic."},{"time":205000,"text":"Of course, the bone in fine-bone china"},{"time":207000,"text":"gives it its translucency"},{"time":209000,"text":"and also its strength,"},{"time":211000,"text":"in order to make these really fine shapes,"},{"time":213000,"text":"like this deer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216000,"text":"In interior decorating, the pig's actually quite there."},{"time":219000,"text":"It's used in paint for the texture,"},{"time":222000,"text":"but also for the glossiness."},{"time":224000,"text":"In sandpaper, bone glue"},{"time":226000,"text":"is actually the glue between the sand and the paper."},{"time":230000,"text":"And then in paintbrushes,"},{"time":232000,"text":"hairs are used because, apparently, they're very suitable for making paintbrushes"},{"time":235000,"text":"because of their hard-wearing nature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238000,"text":"I was not planning on showing you any meat"},{"time":240000,"text":"because, of course, half the book's meat"},{"time":242000,"text":"and you probably all know what meats they are."},{"time":244000,"text":"But I didn't want you to miss out on this one,"},{"time":246000,"text":"because this, well, it's called \"portion-controlled meat cuts.\""},{"time":249000,"text":"And this is actually sold"},{"time":251000,"text":"in the frozen area of the supermarket."},{"time":253000,"text":"And what it is -- it's actually steak."},{"time":255000,"text":"So, this is sold as cow,"},{"time":257000,"text":"but what happens when you slaughter a cow --"},{"time":259000,"text":"at least in industrial factory farming --"},{"time":262000,"text":"they have all these little bits of steak left"},{"time":264000,"text":"that they can't actually sell as steak,"},{"time":266000,"text":"so what they do is they glue them all together"},{"time":269000,"text":"with fibrin from pig blood"},{"time":271000,"text":"into this really large sausage,"},{"time":273000,"text":"then freeze the sausage, cut it in little slices"},{"time":276000,"text":"and sell those as steak again."},{"time":279000,"text":"And this also actually happens with tuna and scallops."},{"time":285000,"text":"So, with the steak, you might drink a beer."},{"time":287000,"text":"In the brewing process, there's lots of cloudy elements in the beer,"},{"time":290000,"text":"so to get rid of these cloudy elements,"},{"time":292000,"text":"what some companies do"},{"time":294000,"text":"is they pour the beer through a sort of gelatin sieve"},{"time":296000,"text":"in order to get rid of that cloudiness."},{"time":299000,"text":"This actually also goes for wine as well as fruit juice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304000,"text":"There's actually a company in Greece"},{"time":306000,"text":"that produces these cigarettes"},{"time":308000,"text":"that actually contain hemoglobin from pigs in the filter."},{"time":311000,"text":"And according to them,"},{"time":313000,"text":"this creates an artificial lung in the filter."},{"time":315000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":317000,"text":"So, this is actually a healthier cigarette."},{"time":320000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":322000,"text":"Injectable collagen -- or, since the '70s, collagen from pigs --"},{"time":325000,"text":"has been used for injecting into wrinkles."},{"time":327000,"text":"And the reason for this is that pigs are actually quite close to human beings,"},{"time":330000,"text":"so the collagen is as well."},{"time":334000,"text":"Well, this must be the strangest thing I found."},{"time":337000,"text":"This is a bullet coming from"},{"time":339000,"text":"a very large ammunition company in the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342000,"text":"And while I was making the book,"},{"time":344000,"text":"I contacted all the producers of products"},{"time":346000,"text":"because I wanted them to send me the real samples"},{"time":348000,"text":"and the real specimens."},{"time":351000,"text":"So I sent this company an email"},{"time":353000,"text":"saying, \"Hello. I'm Christien. I'm doing this research."},{"time":355000,"text":"And can you send me a bullet?\""},{"time":357000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":359000,"text":"And well, I didn't expect them to even answer my email."},{"time":361000,"text":"But they answered"},{"time":363000,"text":"and they said, \"Why, thank you for your email. What an interesting story."},{"time":366000,"text":"Are you in anyway related to the Dutch government?\""},{"time":369000,"text":"I thought that was really weird,"},{"time":371000,"text":"as if the Dutch government sends emails to anyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":378000,"text":"So, the most beautiful thing I found --"},{"time":381000,"text":"at least what I think is the most beautiful -- in the book, is this heart valve."},{"time":384000,"text":"It's actually a very low-tech"},{"time":386000,"text":"and very high-tech product at the same time."},{"time":388000,"text":"The low-tech bit is that it's literally a pig's heart valve"},{"time":391000,"text":"mounted in the high-tech bit,"},{"time":393000,"text":"which is a memory metal casing."},{"time":395000,"text":"And what happens is this can be implanted into a human heart"},{"time":398000,"text":"without open heart surgery."},{"time":400000,"text":"And once it's in the right spot,"},{"time":402000,"text":"they remove the outer shell,"},{"time":404000,"text":"and the heart valve, well, it gets this shape"},{"time":406000,"text":"and at that moment it starts beating, instantly."},{"time":409000,"text":"It's really a sort of magical moment."},{"time":412000,"text":"So this is actually a Dutch company,"},{"time":414000,"text":"so I called them up, and I asked,"},{"time":416000,"text":"\"Can I borrow a heart valve from you?\""},{"time":419000,"text":"And the makers of this thing were really enthusiastic."},{"time":421000,"text":"So they were like, \"Okay, we'll put it in a jar for you with formalin,"},{"time":424000,"text":"and you can borrow it.\""},{"time":426000,"text":"Great -- and then I didn't hear from them for weeks,"},{"time":429000,"text":"so I called,"},{"time":431000,"text":"and I asked, \"What's going on with the heart valve?\""},{"time":433000,"text":"And they said, \"Well the director of the company"},{"time":436000,"text":"decided not to let you borrow this heart valve,"},{"time":438000,"text":"because want his product"},{"time":440000,"text":"to be associated with pigs.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":443000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":446000,"text":"Well, the last product from the book that I'm showing you is renewable energy --"},{"time":449000,"text":"actually, to show that my first question,"},{"time":451000,"text":"if pigs are still used up until the last bit, was still true."},{"time":454000,"text":"Well it is, because everything that can't be used for anything else"},{"time":457000,"text":"is made into a fuel"},{"time":459000,"text":"that can be used as renewable energy source."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463000,"text":"In total, I found 185 products."},{"time":466000,"text":"And what they showed me"},{"time":468000,"text":"is that, well, firstly,"},{"time":470000,"text":"it's at least to say odd"},{"time":472000,"text":"that we don't treat these pigs"},{"time":474000,"text":"as absolute kings and queens."},{"time":477000,"text":"And the second, is that we actually don't have a clue"},{"time":480000,"text":"of what all these products that surround us are made of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483000,"text":"And you might think I'm very fond of pigs,"},{"time":486000,"text":"but actually -- well, I am a little bit --"},{"time":488000,"text":"but I'm more fond"},{"time":490000,"text":"of raw materials in general."},{"time":492000,"text":"And I think that, in order to take better care"},{"time":495000,"text":"of what's behind our products --"},{"time":497000,"text":"so, the livestock, the crops, the plants,"},{"time":500000,"text":"the non-renewable materials,"},{"time":502000,"text":"but also the people that produce these products --"},{"time":505000,"text":"the first step would actually be to know that they are there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}